title: TRIPLE NUTRITION CURL NOURISH HAIRCARE I GARNIER FRUCTIS
description:
Want curls this hydrated, this strong? Garnier Fructis goes beyond hydration with Triple Nutrition Curl Nourish. It infuses 3x the moisture for stronger curls in just one use.* The sulfate¬-free shampoo and conditioner with coconut oil gently cleanse without stripping moisture. The Butter Cream treatment deeply nourishes. Curls are hydrated, frizz-resistant, stronger.

*Using Garnier Fructis Curl Nourish Shampoo, Conditioner & Leave-In Treatment vs non-conditioning shampoo.
